highlights.text: Camila Cabello has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Havana (feat. Young Thug)” is the highest at #1.
“My My My!” by Troye Sivan is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #31.
“Real Friends” by Camila Cabello is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 56 spots at #36.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 56 weeks straight.
